": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Agence France-Presse\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police and customs officers seized just under 10 kilos of herbal cannabis and cannabis resin, \\u20ac20,000 ($21,700) in cash and 48 mobile phones, the source said.\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2563, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris prosecutor Laure Beccuau said in early May that she expected a spike in crimes during the Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2565, \"end\": 2570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.959897978054095e-42, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2678, \"end\": 2683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.959897978054095e-42, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There will be many more tourists,\\\" she told Franceinfo radio.\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2730, \"end\": 2740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Info_(TV_channel)\", \"score\": 0.9103691617325828, \"rank\": 0.07407407407405789, \"text\": \"Franceinfo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Info_(TV_channel)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_Info_(TV_channel)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This means that the criminals will attack these tourists,\\\" she said, pointing to pick-pocketing, housing scams and other crimes.\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2877, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The operation close to the Olympic village targeted a dealing point that police have been monitoring in the run-up to the Olympic Games, which begin on July 26, said another police source.\", \"from\": 2879, \"to\": 3067, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Over the past months police have stepped up operations in Seine-Saint-Denis, where the athletes' village is located.\", \"from\": 3069, \"to\": 3185, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3127, \"end\": 3144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than 14,000 people will be living in the Olympic Village, comprising 82 buildings in the municipalities of Saint-Denis, Saint-Ouen and Ile-Saint-Denis, north of Paris.\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3358, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3232, \"end\": 3247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.969015766014104e-19, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 3352, \"end\": 3357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.959897978054095e-42, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The village is the single biggest new-build Olympics project, located on a site by the river Seine that is a focus for regeneration efforts in the economically deprived suburb of Seine-Saint-Denis.\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3539, \"end\": 3556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0,